paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses a case of cardiac amyloidosis related to beta 2-microglobulin (B2M) and mentions the TTR gene in the context of genetic testing, but no variants in the TTR gene were reported.

challenges: No TTR variants were reported in the paper.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on a case of B2M-related amyloidosis and confirmed the absence of TTR gene variants in the patient.
